0xC_1000_0000  0xC_1FFF_FFFF    PCI Express 2 Mem Space		256MB
0xC_0000_0000  0xC_0FFF_FFFF    PCI Express 1 Mem Space		256MB
0x0_0000_0000  0x0_ffff_ffff    DDR				4GB


